{"tid":1190591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［真係唔撚明］買一送一 同 買二送二 既分別","createTime":"2019-06-07T11:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T11:47:21.000Z","uid":16510,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eff465c19eab27037539ab928c20351aa1d97a21","tid":1190591,"uid":16510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚明<br />\n點解啲人話買二送二 姐係買一送一<br />\n明撚明寫住買二送二 都話 咪姐係買一送一<br />\n屌你咩 <br />\n買兩件會送兩件 但係買一件係發動唔到呢個優惠架<br />\n係發動唔到架on9<br />\n<br />\n同樣道理<br />\n$10/2斤 唔撚代表$5/斤架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點撚解個個人都以為自己開心大發現咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：十蚊兩斤 咪姐係五蚊一斤囉<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十蚊兩斤姐係買親都要兩斤兩斤買 唔撚可以買一斤 <br />\n就係咁簡單 都唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4da603fc984d0407e844161887267e013fbee5","tid":1190591,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"邊啲人會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}